&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Meet Your Future &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Neighbors&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Compensation Analyst at Nextdoor, you will help us invest in our employee community by developing, implementing, maintaining, and continuously improving our compensation programs. You will be a key member of our People team and work directly with employees at all levels, in every function, across our entire organization.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this role you’ll lead and support People team initiatives, conduct market research and analysis, and monitor compliance with legal and regulatory requirements. You&#39;ll also be responsible for developing and maintaining internal tools, analyzing data and metrics, and improving the overall company through insights you surface about our compensation and broader people programs.&lt;/p&gt;
