&lt;p&gt;Nextdoor (NYSE: NXDR) is the essential neighborhood network. Neighbors, public agencies, and businesses use Nextdoor to connect around local information that matters in more than 350,000 neighborhoods across 11 countries. Nextdoor builds innovative technology to foster local community, share important news, and create neighborhood connections at scale. Download the app and join the neighborhood at &lt;a href=&quot;http://nextdoor.com/&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;nextdoor.com&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
